@page
@model Food_Donation_App.Pages.AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About - Food_Donation_App";
}



<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Food_Donation_App.styles.css" asp-append-version="true" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="mt-5">About Food_Donation_App</h2>

        <p>Food donation to restaurants is a crucial area that demands advanced systems to facilitate transactions and effective communication with specialized agencies in the voluntary sector. The presence of programs and applications dedicated to this aspect can contribute significantly to enhancing the performance of these organizations.</p>

        <p>At Food_Donation_App, we recognize the importance of addressing the unique needs of food donation initiatives. Our platform is designed to provide a comprehensive solution that streamlines transactions, facilitates communication with relevant agencies, and ultimately fosters a positive impact on the voluntary sector.</p>

        <h3 class="mt-4">Project Scope</h3>
        <p>The scope of our project is aligned with the goal of advancing food donation processes and improving the overall performance of organizations involved in this noble cause. Key aspects of the project scope include:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Efficient Transaction Processing: Our platform enables seamless and efficient handling of food donation transactions for restaurants.</li>
            <li>Specialized Agency Communication: Food_Donation_App facilitates communication with specialized agencies in the voluntary sector, promoting collaboration and support.</li>
            <li>Programs and Applications: We offer dedicated programs and applications to address the specific needs of food donation initiatives, contributing to significant improvements in organizational performance.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We are committed to creating a technologically advanced and user-friendly environment that empowers organizations involved in food donation. Explore Food_Donation_App to experience the transformative impact of streamlined processes and enhanced communication.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
</body>
</html>
